description:
It's time for... Family Feud (a Mark Goodson / Jew or Not Jew production)! We'll bypass the family nonsense and go straight to the final round. Answer five questions and see if you can get the best score!

We've surveyed 100 Jews...












SURVEY SAYS:


















.box { background-color: black; color: white; text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap; }


